Notes:
->Api for searching users by username sorted by no of followers
http://localhost/search/user/shalugarg

->Api for searching repositories by username
http://localhost/search/repos/shalugarg

->Logging is enabled in the project and you will see them being logged into your
storage/logs/laravel.log file.

->Api is documented and we have used Laravel API Documentation Generator.The document can be found in apidoc.php file in your config folder.

->In case of ample time we can use swagger open api documentation method
for properly documenting the Api's.

->We have created the UI as well for both the screens but not shared.
